                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "P-LI7"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The Li metal foil with a thickness of 3.7",
                "mg/cm2 was sandwiched between two tantalum foils of",
                "different thicknesses. The front tantalum foil was of",
                "thickness 3.9 mg/cm2 and the back tantalum foil was",
                "of 0.025 mm thick, which was sufficient to stop the",
                "proton beam. The incident proton energies are 3, 4, 5,",
                "6 MeV corresponding to 1.12, 2.12, 3.12 and 4.12 MeV",
                "respectively."
              ]
            }
          ],
